Ushobora kumenyekanisha amakuru kubyerekeye ibicuruzwa byawe ukoresheje ibirango bya QR kugirango ubihuze n'ipaki ifunitse igicuruzwa cyawe. Ushobora kongeramo ibirango byinshi ndetse wanabikoresha utanga amakuru atandukanye y'igicuruzwa kimwe ku basomyi batandukanye. Buri gihe ujye uzirikana gutangaza ibirango kugirango ubikoreshe!
